::Demise/EndBringer::

Demise and EndBringer arrive back at the Blackfortress, Demise 
instantly going to the CR chambers. EndBringer opens a comm to anyone 
in the base, having no idea who was in charge without any of the 
leaders here.

"Hey, I have a prisoner," he says while still shocking and attempting 
to crush Double Punch in his tentacles, "I don't know if he's alive, 
but where do I put him?"
